2025-12-18  Robin Stephenson  <robin@aglet.net>

	* sparkweather.org (sparkweather-add-footer,
	sparkweather-hide-footer): Replace sparkweather-show-footer
	with two options for finer footer control. BREAKING CHANGE:
	sparkweather-show-footer removed; use sparkweather-add-footer
	instead for same behaviour.

	* sparkweather.org: Display improvements: dynamic column width
	calculation based on content, optional footer with timestamp and
	location (sparkweather-show-footer), and optional FACE argument
	for time windows (defaults to 'success).

2025-12-17  Robin Stephenson  <robin@aglet.net>

	* sparkweather.org (sparkweather-time-windows): Replace four
	individual hour variables with single configurable time windows
	list, allowing unlimited custom time periods. BREAKING CHANGE:
	Old sparkweather-{lunch,commute}-{start,end}-hour variables
	deprecated but automatically migrated with warning.

	* sparkweather.org: Refactor, and add test suite.

	* README.md: Document sparkweather-time-windows configuration
	interface with examples.

